description: TEHRAN - Alaeddin Borujerdi, a member of the Iranian Parliament, has denounced the latest resolution passed by the International Atomic Energy Agency's (IAEA) Board of Governors regarding Iran's nuclear program as politically motivated.

description: Ancient Persian architecture, as if narrating a story, reveals centuries of conquests, spiritual journeys, and majestic empires that have shaped its landscape.
